{
  "stem": "22856.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I belonged to the student's corporation, they're called, El Al, when I was in the college.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later on, when I went to the university, I advanced to El Al-- to [INAUDIBLE], which was our [INAUDIBLE] Zionist organization-- corporation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother always dreamt, but we didn't see any possibility by that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, there was a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that one of our-- of my boss was visiting-- visited by underground Haganah, but I don't know how that was finished.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the war commenced, everything stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Strictly speaking, my studies finished in March, 1939, but it all started in 1935 when I applied to the Cracow university to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, there was a system in Poland, which was called numerus clausus, which means that 10% of seats were reserved for Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because there were 100 seats in the first year, so only 10 Jews could be accepted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But priority had sons of doctors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, I failed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I picked studies very close to the medicine-- medical [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] faculty, and next year I applied again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time the numerus clausus was cut to 7%, and the same has happened next year.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I applied during the third year, there came a numerus nullus, which means no Jews could study, whether he was the son of a doctor or not.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- by that time we have all information by radio, by press, and some commentaries in the society.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew what's coming, but we couldn't do anything else only to follow what the government decided.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were several parts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's usually leftist, rightist, and centrists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I belonged to the rightists.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
